WEBVTT

1
00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:01.660
Ah, just a week...

2
00:00:01.660 --> 00:00:03.340
That's just how a master's life is,

3
00:00:03.440 --> 00:00:05.200
but perhaps miracles will happen,

4
00:00:05.340 --> 00:00:06.480
Don't worry too much.

5
00:00:06.620 --> 00:00:07.800
Linda, could you help me leave

6
00:00:07.800 --> 00:00:09.320
the manor? I need to find her.

7
00:00:09.420 --> 00:00:10.500
I'm worried about her injuries.

8
00:00:12.300 --> 00:00:12.940
But...

9
00:00:12.940 --> 00:00:13.940
The master said just now,

10
00:00:14.160 --> 00:00:16.160
the manor is hosting a party in three days,

11
00:00:16.280 --> 00:00:17.480
and there will be

12
00:00:17.480 --> 00:00:18.300
many guests.

13
00:00:18.500 --> 00:00:19.240
I'll figure something out,

14
00:00:19.260 --> 00:00:20.280
to get you out with them.

15
00:00:20.580 --> 00:00:21.820
Thank you, Linda.

16
00:00:23.400 --> 00:00:23.720
Come.

17
00:00:26.140 --> 00:00:27.940
Seventh Miss, I've made inquiries,

18
00:00:28.180 --> 00:00:29.040
and at the banquet the day after tomorrow,

19
00:00:29.300 --> 00:00:30.600
the Tamoxi leader will be present.

20
00:00:30.760 --> 00:00:31.420
I have a friend

21
00:00:31.540 --> 00:00:32.820
who works for Tamoxi.

22
00:00:32.860 --> 00:00:34.040
You'll pose as

23
00:00:34.040 --> 00:00:34.600
her escort,

24
00:00:34.880 --> 00:00:36.160
and she'll get you out.

25
00:00:36.780 --> 00:00:38.100
Linda, thank you.

26
00:00:38.600 --> 00:00:39.900
If Huo Jiu Ling finds out you

27
00:00:39.900 --> 00:00:40.820
helped me escape,

28
00:00:40.940 --> 00:00:42.280
will he trouble you?

29
00:00:42.360 --> 00:00:43.600
Seventh Miss, don't worry,

30
00:00:43.800 --> 00:00:44.720
there will be so many

31
00:00:44.720 --> 00:00:45.660
guests at the party,

32
00:00:45.840 --> 00:00:46.900
the master won't know it was

33
00:00:46.900 --> 00:00:47.480
me.

34
00:00:50.120 --> 00:00:50.420
Go.

35
00:00:57.020 --> 00:00:58.200
Is something the matter?

36
00:00:58.340 --> 00:00:59.840
It's the stylist the master arranged,

37
00:01:00.100 --> 00:01:02.160
to style the Seventh Miss.

